SUMMARY:💘 Singles Mixer for Law + Finance Professionals
DESCRIPTION:Connect with likeminded professionals at Toronto’s 1st dedicated singles mixer for law & finance professionals who understand the pressure\, pace & ambition. \nWhen: Tuesday\, March 31\, 2026 | 7:30pm – 10:00pmWhere: Goodman Pub and KitchenTickets: [Buy Here](must buy  ticket from website – RSVP from Meetup doesn’t count) \nWhat to expect at our event: \n\nA dedicated and experienced event host\, emcee and dating coach – Andrea Lo\nIcebreakers and intros\nOpen mingling\nNo match form – old school – connect by asking each other for their contact\n\nCan’t make it? Follow Toronto Dating Hub for upcoming mixers & events!
URL:https://nowtoronto.com/event/%f0%9f%92%98-singles-mixer-for-law-finance-professionals/
LOCATION:The Goodman Pub and Kitchen\, 207 Queens Quay W\, Toronto\, ON M5J 1A7\, Canada\, Old Toronto\, Toronto\, Ontario\, M5J 1A7
CATEGORIES:Community Events,Nightlife
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://nowtoronto.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/f09f9298-singles-mixer-for-law-finance-professionals.png
